    • Method Detail

      • updateSetBeanListFromApi

        public static void updateSetBeanListFromApi()
        This method checks the offical Mtg API for the latest set. If the latest set of the API response and the latest set within the internal SetBean list do net match, the internal SetBean list will be updated with all new sets.

      • getSetBeanList

        public static SetBean[] getSetBeanList()
        This method returns the internal list of SetBean objects as an array.
        Returns:
        Array with all internal SetBean objects.

      • saveSetBeanList

        public static void saveSetBeanList()
        This method saves the current internal list of CardBean objects to the local system. The save destination is defined by property 'url_carddata' in config file 'config/config.properties'.
